frames.caption: A whimsical scene depicts a large strawberry transformed into a fantastical dwelling, complete with wooden structures and small figures resembling construction workers. The figures are actively engaged in various tasks, suggesting a bustling atmosphere. The setting is surreal, blending elements of nature and human ingenuity.
frames.description: The scene presents a fantastical construction site where a giant strawberry serves as the central structure. Wooden platforms and ladders are attached to the strawberry, and small figures in construction attire are busy working around it. The atmosphere is imaginative and playful, evoking a sense of wonder.

frames.caption: A whimsical scene depicts a large strawberry transformed into a fantastical house, complete with wooden structures and glowing windows. Tiny figures dressed as construction workers are actively engaged in building and maintaining this imaginative dwelling. The setting is surreal, blending elements of nature and fantasy in a playful manner.
frames.description: The scene is set in a fantasy world where a strawberry serves as the foundation for a miniature house. The structure is adorned with wooden elements and illuminated windows, creating a cozy atmosphere. Tiny figures, resembling construction workers, are seen working on the strawberry house, adding a sense of activity and creativity to the scene.
